data.description: ***SELLER WILLING TO PAY $5000 USE AS YOU CHOOSE*** Beautiful Like new Home in Willow Pond Subdivision.  4 Bedrooms 2.5 Baths with a Loft.  Upon entering the home, you will see the stunning open floor plan.  Dining Room with trey ceilings.  The kitchen has a magnificent Island and tons of cabinets and counter space.  The kitchen also has a pantry!!  Large living area with fireplace perfect for the whole family.  The back leads through a screen porch to the almost 1-acre lot.  Large 1st floor master with walk in closet. Master Bath with Dual Vanity.  Upstairs are 3 additional bedrooms all with large walk-in closets.  Upstairs is also a Loft that can be used as a playroom or office.  Tons of storage space with the walk in storge room and the pull-down attic space.
